|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@3 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                            |
|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@1 as answer, trunc(score@2, 3) as trunc(vector_search().score,Int64(3)), score@2 as score] |
